  "notes": "Aspect-matched 40x28 (HxW) experiment. SC HUD digits have a natural ~0.6 wide-to-tall aspect; v3's 28x28 square canvas distorts the glyph during the resize step. This model uses a 40-tall x 28-wide canvas so glyphs need less shape distortion. Architecture is a 3-conv + FC RGB CNN matching v3 in spirit (only the FC bottleneck dimension changes from 64*7*7 to 64*10*7 to accommodate the taller feature map). Training corpus is signature-region2 only (no @ class, no panel-font samples) \u2014 apples-to-apples with the digits-only subset of v3."
